Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.81,0:04:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,（本劇開始）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.28,0:04:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我們蔚藍的家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.50,0:05:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,海水百合搖曳的所在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.71,0:05:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我與我無數個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.64,0:05:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,兄弟姊妹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.40,0:05:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,一齊發聲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.03,0:05:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,以泡沫之語
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.08,0:05:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你還記得嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.96,0:05:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,很久很久以前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.55,0:06:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你和我曾生活在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.69,0:06:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,蔚藍的大海之中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.24,0:06:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,水母與海膽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.20,0:06:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,魚兒和螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.66,0:06:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,他們全是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.05,0:06:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你的手足
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.15,0:06:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,宗介，要快點回來喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.99,0:06:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.55,0:08:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,金魚耶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.81,0:08:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,拿不出來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.66,0:09:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.42,0:09:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.55,0:09:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,死掉了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.52,0:09:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,她舔了我，還活著耶！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.44,0:09:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,宗介，要出門囉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.27,0:09:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,理莎，金魚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.83,0:09:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,真奇怪的風，宗介，我先去熱車了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.22,0:10:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,找到了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.06,0:10:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼？她被人類抓走了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.27,0:10:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,糟了，這下糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.09,0:10:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,死掉了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.85,0:10:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,還活著！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.66,0:11:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,宗介，要遲到了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.08,0:11:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,理莎，金魚還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.20,0:11:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,金魚？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.91,0:11:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我在海邊撿到的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.98,0:11:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道你是哪位\N請不要在這裡撒農藥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.99,0:11:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,這不是農藥，只是怕太乾燥了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.33,0:11:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,這可是深海裡的淨水
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.95,0:11:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,如果不是農藥的話就好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.12,0:11:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.55,0:12:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,糟糕，越來越不妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.26,0:12:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的，真是個怪人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.10,0:12:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,但不能說他是怪人喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.89,0:12:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,因為不能以貌取人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.48,0:12:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我不會這麼說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.06,0:12:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你要帶她去幼稚園嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.57,0:12:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,老師會答應嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.44,0:12:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,沒問題的，我會保護妳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.28,0:12:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,很可愛嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.66,0:12:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,今天船會到港
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.00,0:12:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,到學校前把早餐吃完吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.75,0:12:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道她吃不吃這個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.55,0:12:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,要吃嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.30,0:12:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,咦？傷口不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.72,0:12:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,理莎，她叫做波妞喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.23,0:13:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,因為她像水波一樣軟軟的\N又會用魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.94,0:13:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,被波妞舔過後傷口就好了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.83,0:13:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,要吃火腿嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.72,0:13:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,理莎，波妞喜歡吃火腿耶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.26,0:13:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我一樣耶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.33,0:14:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.58,0:14:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,真髒，有夠髒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.50,0:14:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,理莎太太，快點！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.26,0:14:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,真髒，有夠髒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.89,0:14:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.03,0:14:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,波妞妳看，看得到我們家喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.41,0:14:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,早安！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.47,0:14:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,停在這邊好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.43,0:14:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.34,0:14:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.51,0:14:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我去上課了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.43,0:15:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,早安，對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.97,0:15:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,-麻煩妳推一下紀子婆婆的輪椅\N-好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.41,0:15:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,早安呀，小宗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.20,0:15:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,芳江婆婆，我現在很忙\N等一下再聊喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.12,0:15:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,唉呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.46,0:15:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,小宗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.08,0:15:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,-辰婆婆，等一下再聊喔\N-唉呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.72,0:15:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,老師會不會不准啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.93,0:15:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我決定了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.10,0:15:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,在這邊等我，我馬上就回來喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.65,0:15:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道會不會有貓跑過來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.12,0:16:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,要乖乖待在這裡喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.91,0:16:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我馬上回來喲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.34,0:16:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,再見，唉呀，小敏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.59,0:16:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然有點發燒，不過沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.22,0:16:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,那就拜託妳了，拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.93,0:16:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,老師早安
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.77,0:16:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,早安呀，小宗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.14,0:16:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,小宗，你好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.73,0:16:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,宗介！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.19,0:16:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,久美子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.11,0:16:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你看，漂亮嗎？媽媽買給我的！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.78,0:16:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,宗介，我們去玩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.62,0:16:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我現在很忙，不要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.79,0:16:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你在這裡做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.41,0:16:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,總之我很忙啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.33,0:16:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,宗介真怪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.17,0:16:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.73,0:17:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,波妞！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.49,0:17:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,宗介！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.45,0:17:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,久美子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.45,0:17:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.00,0:17:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以隨便帶東西來學校耶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.58,0:17:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,誰說的，這棵樹不屬於幼稚園的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.63,0:17:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我看啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.17,0:17:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,是金魚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.88,0:17:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不是金魚啦，是波妞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.17,0:17:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,波妞？我想看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.80,0:17:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,給妳看的話不可以告訴別人喔？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.89,0:17:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯，我會保密
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.27,0:17:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,妳看，很可愛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.48,0:17:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,又怪又胖，我家的金魚比較可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.84,0:18:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,是她不好，誰叫她要說波妞的壞話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.89,0:18:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我幫妳加水喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.17,0:18:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,波妞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.34,0:19:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.64,0:19:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.68,0:19:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼好像聽到小宗的聲音呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.02,0:19:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,不過小宗應該在上課啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.57,0:19:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,是幻聽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.82,0:19:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,芳江婆婆，我在喔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.49,0:19:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,唉呀，小宗在呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.49,0:19:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我有沒有帶什麼好東西來呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.75,0:19:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,-有！\N-猜對了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.67,0:19:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什麼顏色的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.92,0:19:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,-嗯，紅色？\N-紅色
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.22,0:19:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.43,0:19:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,妳們怎麼會知道呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.68,0:19:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,-讓我看\N-讓我看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.18,0:19:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.14,0:19:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,唉呀，真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.69,0:19:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.40,0:19:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,她叫做波妞，喜歡火腿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.81,0:20:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,還會魔法喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.86,0:20:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,這邊的傷口被波妞舔過就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.87,0:20:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道能不能也舔舔我們的腳呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.66,0:20:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,要是能再像小宗那樣奔跑就好了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.46,0:20:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,那得問問波妞囉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.96,0:20:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,也給我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.17,0:20:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,好呀，辰婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.47,0:20:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,討厭，這不是人面魚嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.05,0:20:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,快把牠放回海裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.14,0:20:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不然會招來海嘯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.14,0:20:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,辰婆婆又再說什麼海嘯了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.31,0:20:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,傳說人面魚一上岸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.40,0:20:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,就會有海嘯啊，以前人都這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.49,0:20:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,海嘯啊，海嘯來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.53,0:20:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,海嘯來了啊，海嘯！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.16,0:20:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了，辰婆婆？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.79,0:21:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,啊，衣服毀了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.05,0:21:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,宗介
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.56,0:21:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,宗介
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.94,0:21:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,宗介
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.40,0:21:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,宗介
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.53,0:21:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,快跟辰婆婆道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.45,0:21:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不用擔心喔，我一定會保護妳的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.25,0:21:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,宗介
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.17,0:21:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,宗介
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.72,0:21:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,波妞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.43,0:22:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,波妞，宗介
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.48,0:22:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,波妞喜歡宗介！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.15,0:22:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我也喜歡波妞！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.11,0:22:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,波妞喜歡宗介
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.41,0:22:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,波妞！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.20,0:23:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,波妞！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.75,0:23:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,波妞？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.29,0:23:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,波妞！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.80,0:23:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,-波妞！\N-宗介！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.34,0:23:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,波妞！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.80,0:23:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,波妞！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.55,0:23:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,波妞！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.27,0:23:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,波妞
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.95,0:24:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,宗介，你知道有所謂命運一事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.16,0:24:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,就算難過也不能改變命運的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.33,0:24:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,波妞因為出生於海洋
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.62,0:24:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,所以得回到那裡去
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.08,0:24:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,那個灑農藥的男人是很詭異沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.80,0:24:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,給我吃一口
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.92,0:24:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你看，都滴下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.76,0:24:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,很好吃嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.35,0:24:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,打起精神來，今天耕一會回來
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.69,0:24:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,宗介要是沒精神的話，他會失望的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.97,0:25:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,今天不要再去海邊了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.05,0:25:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.58,0:25:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,宗介
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.00,0:25:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,快進來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.13,0:25:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,如果把水桶放在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.92,0:25:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,波妞再來的話\N就會知道這是我們家吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.96,0:26:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,也對，宗介想放的話就放吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.23,0:26:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,宗介你先接一下，一定是耕一
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.15,0:26:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.53,0:26:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,對，我是宗介
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.16,0:26:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,（小金井丸）
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.08,0:26:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯，很好呀
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.12,0:26:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我今天不能回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.16,0:26:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,但我會通過港口，拜託你打信號囉
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.67,0:26:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯，我把電話給理莎聽
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.38,0:26:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,耕一，嗯，什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.09,0:26:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你拒絕不就好了？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.55,0:26:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,就這樣把老婆小孩丟在山上不管！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.55,0:26:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,哼！我不理你了！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.56,0:26:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,宗介，我們今天到外面吃！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.81,0:26:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要在家裡吃
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.30,0:27:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,是耕一！\N理莎，是耕一的船，快關燈
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.08,0:27:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,是宗介！真是個天才
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.50,0:27:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,他才五歲耶
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.21,0:28:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你老婆在生氣吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.67,0:28:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.26,0:28:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,理莎，他說對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.43,0:28:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,笨蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.47,0:28:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.06,0:28:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}笨…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.74,0:28:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,理莎，他說他愛妳！
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.74,0:28:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,他說很愛很愛妳
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.08,0:28:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}（笨蛋…）
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.75,0:28:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,哇，好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.14,0:28:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}（一路順風）
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.85,0:28:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}（謝謝）
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.81,0:29:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}（晚安）
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.58,0:29:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,理莎，不要哭
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.84,0:29:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不會哭的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.75,0:29:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我答應波妞說要保護她的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.18,0:29:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道波妞是不是在哭呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.14,0:29:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,好，我要打起精神囉
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.52,0:29:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我很有精神
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.07,0:29:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.57,0:29:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你也要打起精神
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.28,0:29:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,波妞也會跟理莎一樣沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.41,0:30:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,那吃飯吧，連耕一的份也一起吃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.92,0:30:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我怎麼會做出這種蠢事？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.76,0:30:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不該帶妳們來看農場的工作的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.14,0:30:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,人類的水和空氣是多麼地骯髒
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.69,0:30:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是說過很多次嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.02,0:30:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,來，吃了這個
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.73,0:30:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,妳有在聽嗎，布倫希爾蒂？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.82,0:30:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我要火腿
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.32,0:30:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,火…火腿！
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.74,0:30:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,妳從哪裡知道那可怕的東西？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.99,0:30:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,快說啊，布倫希爾蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.08,0:30:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我才不叫布倫希爾蒂，我叫波妞
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.67,0:30:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,波…波妞？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.50,0:30:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,波妞喜歡宗介
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.13,0:30:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,波妞要變成人類
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.59,0:30:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,變成人類？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.09,0:30:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,那種愚蠢又可憎的生物哪裡好了？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.80,0:30:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,人類只會從大海奪走生命罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.35,0:31:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我也曾是人類
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.44,0:31:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,為了放棄當人，妳知道我花了多少…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.06,0:31:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,波妞想要手
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.82,0:31:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我不要這樣的腳
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.15,0:31:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要有像宗介一樣的腳
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.24,0:31:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,妳不要鬧了！
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.05,0:31:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,長出手了！長出腳了！
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.18,0:31:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,長出來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.22,0:31:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,妳難道舔了人類的血液？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.85,0:31:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我要去找宗介
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.44,0:31:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不行！都是因為汙染喚起劣等基因！
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.48,0:31:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,快變回去…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.87,0:32:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,變回去…回去！
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.75,0:32:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不行！力量不夠！
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.34,0:32:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我要出去！
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.97,0:32:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我要出去…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.60,0:32:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我出去！
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.89,0:32:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,邪惡的血啊，沉靜下來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.35,0:32:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,變小…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.36,0:32:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,不愧是那個人的孩子啊，真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.37,0:32:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,要是妳能一直都這樣無邪就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.52,0:33:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我的能力只能鎮住一時
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.69,0:33:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,還是得叫她來了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.54,0:33:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不行，那能量對你們來說太強了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.67,0:33:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,噓，不行
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.00,0:33:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,真危險，阻擋螃蟹的結界變脆弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.21,0:33:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,差點讓生態界要失衡了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.59,0:33:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,冷靜
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.80,0:33:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,想到要見她，就讓我緊張了起來
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.68,0:33:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,糟糕，這個提煉好了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.27,0:33:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡沒鬆開吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.78,0:34:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有鎖緊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.79,0:34:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下得修理了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.38,0:34:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,連一隻海蟑螂跑進去都是件大事
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.86,0:34:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,做得太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.41,0:34:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,海洋能量正完全滲透進基因中
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.58,0:34:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,當這口井注滿時，海洋的時代會再臨
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.96,0:34:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,生命的爆發將可以匹敵寒武紀
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.25,0:35:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,可憎的人類的時代要結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.09,0:35:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,鬆開了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.72,0:36:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,牙齒！
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.10,0:36:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,-唉呀！\N-唉呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.27,0:36:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我要去找宗介！
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.90,0:36:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,宗介！
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.93,0:39:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,龍捲風！船長，那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.56,0:39:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,是海嘯啊，讓船乘上浪！
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.35,0:39:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.74,0:39:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,船長，無線雷達也沒用！
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.53,0:39:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,有個跟宗介差不多大的女孩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.13,0:39:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,-拜拜\N-再見
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.84,0:39:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,受妳照顧了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.18,0:39:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.89,0:40:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,小宗要不要待在這邊等一下？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.47,0:40:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,老師陪你過去
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.10,0:40:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係，我鑽捷徑過去，老師再見
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.60,0:40:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.52,0:40:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,小心點喔
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.03,0:40:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,啊，宗介對不起，門打不開吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.03,0:40:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,因為停電了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.53,0:41:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,-幼稚園還好嗎？\N-嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.49,0:41:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,理莎
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.20,0:41:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係了，妳可以先走
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.99,0:41:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不過金子太太還沒來吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.75,0:41:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係啦，只是晚一點而已
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.50,0:41:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,反正我們今晚要留下
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.21,0:41:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,妳趁回得去時，快回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.00,0:41:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,宗介，等我一下喔
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.30,0:41:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.98,0:41:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,芳江婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.10,0:41:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,唉呀，是小宗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.82,0:41:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,黑漆漆的看不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.07,0:41:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,那個啊，這個給妳
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.78,0:41:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,唉呀，是什麼呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.78,0:41:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,也給紀子婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.58,0:41:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你呀
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.25,0:41:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,太黑了，什麼都看不見啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.87,0:41:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,因為這種風雨就停電
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.75,0:41:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我才不想要在這裡過夜
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.13,0:42:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,電來了，太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.26,0:42:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好亮呀，是金魚！
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.14,0:42:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,一定是因小宗來了，就有電了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.81,0:42:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,突然形成的輕颱
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.81,0:42:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,持續著強勁風雨…
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.57,0:42:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,真是台爛電視啊
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.73,0:42:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,連氣象也亂報一通
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.61,0:42:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,根本就不準嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.61,0:42:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,小宗，你趕快回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.20,0:42:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,有了金魚護身符，我們就不怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.16,0:42:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.84,0:42:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,也給辰婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.22,0:42:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,皺巴巴的，這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.93,0:42:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,是這樣看啦
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.39,0:42:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了，是蚱蜢
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.48,0:42:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不是啦，是小金井丸號啦
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.73,0:42:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,是小宗爸爸的船吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.82,0:42:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.73,0:43:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,可是看起來像蚱蜢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.24,0:43:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,宗介，要走了，跟大家說再見吧
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.70,0:43:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯，大家再見
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.83,0:43:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,-再見\N-再見
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.50,0:43:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,不要被風吹走囉
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.00,0:43:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,從這邊上去
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.30,0:43:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,電話好像也打不通
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.87,0:43:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,海浪好大喔
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.96,0:43:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,船會不會沉下去呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.63,0:44:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,出外海的話，船就不怕風浪了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.42,0:44:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,耕一也一定出外海了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.73,0:44:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,有魚耶，理莎，有魚
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.98,0:44:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,繫好安全帶！
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.23,0:44:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,（第12大濱丸）
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.28,0:44:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,理莎太太，這邊已經過不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.45,0:44:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,剛剛已經發布避難命令了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.24,0:44:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,避難？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.54,0:44:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,還留在向日葵之家的婆婆怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.04,0:44:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,那是島的另一邊，堤防又高\N沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.50,0:44:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,總之我非得先回家一趟不可
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.59,0:44:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,-這邊不能過啊\N-請妳繞山路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.97,0:44:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,宗介，要衝了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.31,0:44:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,-啊，不行啊\N-大浪要來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.23,0:45:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,要來了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.36,0:45:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,快逃啊，理莎太太
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.73,0:45:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,魚跟來了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.19,0:45:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,繫好安全帶，宗介！
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.50,0:46:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,好，要衝了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.43,0:46:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,真是纏人的海浪
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.82,0:47:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,有一個女孩掉下去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.82,0:47:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,剛剛她在魚的上面！
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.58,0:47:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.84,0:47:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,水位越來越高了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.46,0:47:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,宗介，你在哪裡看到那個小女孩的？
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.13,0:47:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,剛才她在那邊的魚的上面跑
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.93,0:47:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,魚？
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.64,0:47:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,宗介，走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.99,0:48:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,加油，就快到家了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.76,0:48:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,有個小女孩！
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.18,0:49:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,危險啊，過來這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.76,0:49:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,宗介，你待在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.25,0:49:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,宗介，你認識她嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.73,0:49:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,波妞？
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.94,0:49:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯！我是波妞！
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.40,0:49:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,是波妞
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.57,0:50:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,理莎，波妞變成女生回來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.84,0:50:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我找到宗介了！
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.23,0:50:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,聽好喔，宗介和波妞
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.36,0:50:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,不管你們覺得多不可思議、多興奮
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.20,0:50:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,都先冷靜下來，好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.20,0:50:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,-嗯\N-嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.41,0:50:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,乖孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.37,0:50:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,宗介，你先把雨衣脫下來
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.08,0:50:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,波妞沒穿鞋啊？拿著這個一下
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.34,0:51:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我去拿東西來給你們擦
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.74,0:51:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,波妞，這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.32,0:51:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,哇，有宗介的味道！
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.24,0:51:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,-好痛\N-波妞！
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.88,0:51:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,抓到了！不能這樣溼答答的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.63,0:51:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,波妞有一頭漂亮的紅髮耶，咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.85,0:51:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,妳衣服沒有濕耶
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.89,0:51:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,因為波妞本來是魚呀，濕了也不怕
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.56,0:52:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯，波妞喜歡這個
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.65,0:52:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,好，我們來喝茶吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.07,0:52:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,波妞，照明麻煩妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.61,0:52:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.45,0:52:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,那會不會有水呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.74,0:52:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,-有水\N-有水！
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.08,0:52:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,-流出來了\N-流出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.29,0:52:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,因為山坡上有水槽的關係啊
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.55,0:52:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,有沒有瓦斯呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.84,0:52:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,點燃！
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.38,0:52:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,-太棒了！\N-太棒了！
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.51,0:52:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,因為是天然氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.18,0:52:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,好，請過去坐下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.73,0:52:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.02,0:52:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,波妞，是這邊喔！
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.82,0:52:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,要這樣坐喔
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.41,0:52:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,腳要放下面喔
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.62,0:52:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣就不能用手了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.50,0:52:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我有腳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.04,0:53:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.42,0:53:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,哇，你們在幹嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.59,0:53:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,波妞的腳可以像手一樣動耶
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.99,0:53:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,請用
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.00,0:53:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.59,0:54:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,呼，真好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.51,0:54:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,那接下來要幹嘛呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.89,0:54:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,波妞想要吃火腿
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.64,0:54:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,波妞最喜歡火腿了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.35,0:54:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,吃飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.65,0:54:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不過得先去發動發電機
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.94,0:54:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,要有電才能連絡耕一
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.20,0:54:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,耕一是我爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.82,0:54:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,是一個壞魔法師嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.70,0:54:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.03,0:54:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,他是小金井丸號的船長喔
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.79,0:55:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,波妞的爸爸呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.08,0:55:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,他叫藤本，他都把我關起來
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.00,0:55:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,波妞是逃出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.71,0:55:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,波妞的媽媽呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.72,0:55:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,波妞最喜歡媽媽了！
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.39,0:55:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,她超級可怕的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.01,0:55:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,跟理莎一樣耶
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.35,0:55:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,波妞，拜託妳囉
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.25,0:55:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,汽油不能用了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.54,0:55:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,堵住了？
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.88,0:55:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,堵住了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.21,0:55:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,那邊堵住了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.48,0:56:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.06,0:56:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,好亮！
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.77,0:56:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,波妞好厲害！
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.50,0:56:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,天線！
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.42,0:56:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,理莎，大家是不是都沉下去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.76,0:56:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,一點燈光都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.99,0:56:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,好吵
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.86,0:56:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,連不上嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.99,0:57:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,訊號好像連不上
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.66,0:57:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,這邊是ＪＡ4ＬＬ
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.17,0:57:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,耕一聽得到嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.13,0:57:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡是理莎、宗介和波妞
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.80,0:57:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我們一切都好
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.84,0:57:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我們等一下要吃飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:57:19.55,0:57:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,火腿
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.73,0:57:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,放進去了嗎？小心很燙喔
Dialogue: 0,0:57:48.96,0:57:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,還沒好喔
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.96,0:57:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,要等三分鐘喔
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.52,0:58:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,請閉上眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.10,0:58:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,還不行喔
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.02,0:58:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,波妞，眼睛閉起來
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.74,0:58:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,好，可以了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.53,0:58:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,快吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.17,0:58:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,-有火腿！\N-太好了，波妞
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.09,0:58:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,好燙…
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.27,0:58:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,理莎，波妞睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.66,0:59:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,波妞是不是從很遠的地方來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.03,0:59:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯，應該是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.68,0:59:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,宗介你看，海浪平靜下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.56,0:59:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,可能是因為波妞睡著了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.18,0:59:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,宗介，那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:59:39.73,0:59:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,有光在動，有人在那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.78,0:59:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是芳江婆婆她們？
Dialogue: 0,0:59:51.20,0:59:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.54,0:59:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,是山上的路
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.83,0:59:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,宗介，你陪在波妞身邊
Dialogue: 0,1:00:11.27,1:00:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,現在繞過山路的話，也許過得去
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.15,1:00:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,宗介，我要去一下向日葵之家
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.77,1:00:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我也要去！
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.19,1:00:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,宗介和波妞待在家裡
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.11,1:00:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我還是要去，帶波妞一起去就好了
Dialogue: 0,1:00:29.41,1:00:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我們跟理莎一起去
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.25,1:00:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,現在這個家就像暴風雨中的燈塔
Dialogue: 0,1:00:37.17,1:00:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,黑暗中的人們\N都依靠著這光芒取得溫暖
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.34,1:00:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,所以一定要有人留著
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.21,1:00:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然發生了很多無法理解的事
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.47,1:00:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,無法知道答案
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.09,1:00:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,但很快就會瞭解的
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.05,1:00:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,現在我比較擔心養老院的人
Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.31,1:00:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你幫我守著家的話，我也會有力量
Dialogue: 0,1:00:58.52,1:01:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係的，我一定會回來的
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.15,1:01:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,一定？
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.44,1:01:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,一定
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.95,1:01:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,一定喔
Dialogue: 0,1:01:09.45,1:01:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我最喜歡宗介了
Dialogue: 0,1:02:05.84,1:02:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,月亮出來了，看得到村子的燈火
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.34,1:02:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,感謝老天，這樣就可以找方位了
Dialogue: 0,1:02:12.72,1:02:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,沒看過這村子
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.94,1:02:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是漂到美國來了啊？
Dialogue: 0,1:02:41.50,1:02:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,那不是山，也不是港
Dialogue: 0,1:02:45.13,1:02:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,全是船！
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.60,1:02:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,那些船被海水沖積，堆成一座山了
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.14,1:03:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,那一定是船的墳場\N通往冥界的門開了！
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.65,1:03:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,引擎停了！
Dialogue: 0,1:03:11.07,1:03:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,讓船停在海面上！下錨！
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.16,1:03:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,1:03:28.75,1:03:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,後面有什麼要來了！
Dialogue: 0,1:03:58.45,1:03:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我看到觀世音菩薩了，啊！
Dialogue: 0,1:04:10.80,1:04:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,-可以動了\N-得救了
Dialogue: 0,1:04:13.17,1:04:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,菩薩啊，一定是菩薩幫忙
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.47,1:04:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,南無…
Dialogue: 0,1:04:47.21,1:04:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,再高一點
Dialogue: 0,1:05:02.39,1:05:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,居然設了結界
Dialogue: 0,1:05:04.93,1:05:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,她是在哪學會這些的！
Dialogue: 0,1:05:25.08,1:05:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然還變成人類
Dialogue: 0,1:05:28.29,1:05:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,哇，危險，你們在幹嘛！
Dialogue: 0,1:05:40.01,1:05:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,是妳們！啊，危險！
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.02,1:05:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,住手啊！
Dialogue: 0,1:05:54.82,1:05:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,妳們，爸爸是為姊姊著想…
Dialogue: 0,1:06:03.41,1:06:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,是她！她來了
Dialogue: 0,1:06:43.28,1:06:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,藤本
Dialogue: 0,1:06:44.74,1:06:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,妳終於來了
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.70,1:06:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,真美的海
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.46,1:06:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,充滿魔力
Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.84,1:06:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,就像回歸了泥盆紀的海
Dialogue: 0,1:06:58.88,1:07:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,波妞喝了人類的血
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.34,1:07:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,還把我存下的生命之水全用盡了
Dialogue: 0,1:07:05.39,1:07:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,波妞，有人替她取了個好名字
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.81,1:07:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,是我的錯
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.15,1:07:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,波妞亂用魔力，搗亂了世界
Dialogue: 0,1:07:21.86,1:07:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,她不知道自己正在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:07:24.86,1:07:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,而且還變成人類
Dialogue: 0,1:07:26.32,1:07:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,跑到人類的男朋友家去
Dialogue: 0,1:07:31.00,1:07:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣放任她的話，世界會毀滅啊！
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.43,1:07:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不行！連人工衛星都開始落下了
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.43,1:07:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,行星重力場崩壞的第二個階段
Dialogue: 0,1:07:50.10,1:07:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,藤本，安靜
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.07,1:08:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,宗介，那男孩叫做宗介呀？
Dialogue: 0,1:08:06.41,1:08:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,妳們最喜歡姊姊，是吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.75,1:08:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,老公，就讓波妞當人類吧
Dialogue: 0,1:08:18.21,1:08:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,那古老的魔法
Dialogue: 0,1:08:20.17,1:08:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,只要那男生不變心\N波妞就會失去魔力變成人
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.26,1:08:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,但那個方法是
Dialogue: 0,1:08:27.43,1:08:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,要是失敗的話，波妞就會變成泡沫啊
Dialogue: 0,1:08:30.14,1:08:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我們本來也是從泡沫誕生的啊
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.02,1:08:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,-但是他才五歲耶，不行啦\N-噓！
Dialogue: 0,1:08:42.23,1:08:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,現在就安靜的睡吧，小朋友們
Dialogue: 0,1:08:58.92,1:08:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,宗介！
Dialogue: 0,1:09:01.54,1:09:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,宗介
Dialogue: 0,1:09:08.30,1:09:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,波妞，早安
Dialogue: 0,1:09:10.30,1:09:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,宗介，早安
Dialogue: 0,1:09:18.85,1:09:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,變成海洋了
Dialogue: 0,1:09:44.88,1:09:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,理莎不在耶
Dialogue: 0,1:09:46.84,1:09:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,因為路被淹住了
Dialogue: 0,1:09:49.09,1:09:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,要是有船就好了
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.10,1:09:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,有船呀
Dialogue: 0,1:09:58.77,1:10:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,可是又不能乘坐
Dialogue: 0,1:10:00.15,1:10:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,1:10:17.54,1:10:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,變大了！
Dialogue: 0,1:10:21.75,1:10:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,連蠟燭都變大了
Dialogue: 0,1:10:23.75,1:10:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,可以乘坐喔
Dialogue: 0,1:10:25.34,1:10:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯，好厲害喔
Dialogue: 0,1:10:26.67,1:10:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,很厲害耶
Dialogue: 0,1:10:28.05,1:10:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,幫我搬那邊
Dialogue: 0,1:10:29.42,1:10:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,1:10:32.97,1:10:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,可以了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:10:34.51,1:10:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,可以了
Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.78,1:10:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,浮起來了！
Dialogue: 0,1:10:52.86,1:10:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼多水也不會滲進來
Dialogue: 0,1:10:55.41,1:10:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,對了，要讓管子進水
Dialogue: 0,1:10:58.62,1:11:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,要讓水進去這裡
Dialogue: 0,1:11:01.46,1:11:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,到這個圓圓的地方喔
Dialogue: 0,1:11:31.49,1:11:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,好像火箭
Dialogue: 0,1:11:40.37,1:11:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,波妞，好棒喔
Dialogue: 0,1:11:41.96,1:11:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒？
Dialogue: 0,1:11:44.29,1:11:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,-好棒？\N-好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:11:46.46,1:11:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒…
Dialogue: 0,1:12:07.19,1:12:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,（安全火柴）
Dialogue: 0,1:12:12.19,1:12:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,很燙嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:12:13.40,1:12:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,好燙
Dialogue: 0,1:12:18.70,1:12:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,-好燙！\N-好燙！
Dialogue: 0,1:12:24.12,1:12:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,哇，點起來了
Dialogue: 0,1:12:25.67,1:12:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,點起來了！
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.04,1:12:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,好燙！
Dialogue: 0,1:12:38.09,1:12:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,很燙吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.90,1:12:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,會動了
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.99,1:12:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,宗介，好棒喔
Dialogue: 0,1:12:57.07,1:12:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,-真棒\N-嗯
Dialogue: 0,1:13:06.33,1:13:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,-宗介，好開心喔\N-嗯
Dialogue: 0,1:13:09.71,1:13:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,-宗介，蠟燭在燒耶\N-嗯
Dialogue: 0,1:13:12.75,1:13:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,宗介，很燙吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:13:15.67,1:13:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,波妞負責看守前面，我來掌舵
Dialogue: 0,1:13:19.89,1:13:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯，波妞來看守
Dialogue: 0,1:13:48.58,1:13:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,有路耶
Dialogue: 0,1:13:50.25,1:13:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,是理莎走過的山路喔
Dialogue: 0,1:13:54.75,1:13:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,理莎不在耶
Dialogue: 0,1:13:56.80,1:13:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,理莎一定會在，因為她答應過我了
Dialogue: 0,1:14:05.01,1:14:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,是古代魚，泥盆紀的海洋生物耶
Dialogue: 0,1:14:08.39,1:14:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,那是溝鱗魚啦
Dialogue: 0,1:14:15.73,1:14:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,這個是…
Dialogue: 0,1:14:17.03,1:14:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,泥盆世肺魚！
Dialogue: 0,1:14:18.11,1:14:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,泥盆世肺魚！
Dialogue: 0,1:14:19.78,1:14:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,哇，好大
Dialogue: 0,1:14:22.28,1:14:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,那是帝玻鯰克斯啦
Dialogue: 0,1:14:24.20,1:14:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,帝玻鯰克斯！
Dialogue: 0,1:14:32.75,1:14:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,1:14:38.38,1:14:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,有船！
Dialogue: 0,1:14:40.34,1:14:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,1:14:43.30,1:14:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,他們在叫我們
Dialogue: 0,1:14:46.18,1:14:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,1:14:53.44,1:14:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,奇怪？
Dialogue: 0,1:14:58.28,1:14:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道怎麼弄了
Dialogue: 0,1:15:03.41,1:15:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,波妞，可以了
Dialogue: 0,1:15:11.29,1:15:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,-你們好\N-妳好
Dialogue: 0,1:15:13.54,1:15:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,唉呀，真是艘好船
Dialogue: 0,1:15:16.42,1:15:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我還想說是誰\N原來是理莎的兒子小宗呀
Dialogue: 0,1:15:19.71,1:15:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不是小宗啦，是宗介
Dialogue: 0,1:15:22.43,1:15:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,她叫波妞
Dialogue: 0,1:15:24.89,1:15:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,波妞本來是魚
Dialogue: 0,1:15:27.43,1:15:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,魚？
Dialogue: 0,1:15:29.64,1:15:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,波妞真是個好名字
Dialogue: 0,1:15:31.93,1:15:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,1:15:33.85,1:15:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,叔叔，你有看到理莎嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:15:35.94,1:15:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,理莎太太？
Dialogue: 0,1:15:38.36,1:15:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你們沒有在一起嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:15:40.11,1:15:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,她去向日葵之家了
Dialogue: 0,1:15:41.57,1:15:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,去向日葵之家啊？
Dialogue: 0,1:15:43.11,1:15:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,這是小寶寶喔
Dialogue: 0,1:16:14.60,1:16:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,唉呀，怎麼啦？
Dialogue: 0,1:16:23.74,1:16:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,妳要給我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:16:38.63,1:16:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,借我一下
Dialogue: 0,1:16:45.22,1:16:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,1:16:46.97,1:16:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我不客氣囉
Dialogue: 0,1:16:52.52,1:16:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,哇，真好喝的湯！
Dialogue: 0,1:16:54.77,1:16:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,那是理莎煮的
Dialogue: 0,1:16:57.10,1:16:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,要給小寶寶喝的
Dialogue: 0,1:17:00.19,1:17:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起，小寶寶還不能喝湯
Dialogue: 0,1:17:04.49,1:17:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,但我喝了就可以給寶寶喝奶囉
Dialogue: 0,1:17:10.70,1:17:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是喝理莎的奶奶長大的
Dialogue: 0,1:17:13.58,1:17:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,波妞，我可以喝掉這個湯嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:17:16.91,1:17:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯，可以啊
Dialogue: 0,1:17:19.42,1:17:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,1:17:38.14,1:17:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,是村裡的人，好像船的祭典一樣
Dialogue: 0,1:17:42.02,1:17:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,喂，你們有什麼要幫忙的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:17:46.90,1:17:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝，目前沒問題
Dialogue: 0,1:17:52.33,1:17:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,請你們跟在船隊後面
Dialogue: 0,1:17:54.91,1:17:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,往山上的旅館移動
Dialogue: 0,1:17:58.16,1:18:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,是，了解
Dialogue: 0,1:18:02.88,1:18:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,好多人喔
Dialogue: 0,1:18:04.30,1:18:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了，大家都沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,1:18:06.96,1:18:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,波妞，要點火囉
Dialogue: 0,1:18:08.38,1:18:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下，那個…
Dialogue: 0,1:18:16.14,1:18:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,變成奶奶喔
Dialogue: 0,1:18:18.10,1:18:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,唉呀
Dialogue: 0,1:18:20.56,1:18:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,奶奶！
Dialogue: 0,1:18:21.81,1:18:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,火腿都被波妞吃掉了
Dialogue: 0,1:18:24.48,1:18:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝，一定會變成好喝的奶奶的
Dialogue: 0,1:18:27.49,1:18:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,宗介
Dialogue: 0,1:18:29.40,1:18:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然這是用剩的，你要不要？
Dialogue: 0,1:18:31.78,1:18:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯，波妞會把它變大的，謝謝
Dialogue: 0,1:18:36.33,1:18:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,-小心點喔\N-謝謝你們喔
Dialogue: 0,1:18:44.92,1:18:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了呀？
Dialogue: 0,1:18:51.01,1:18:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,好乖
Dialogue: 0,1:19:11.70,1:19:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,波妞
Dialogue: 0,1:19:26.09,1:19:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,小宗
Dialogue: 0,1:19:27.25,1:19:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,是小宗！
Dialogue: 0,1:19:28.59,1:19:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,唉呀
Dialogue: 0,1:19:29.59,1:19:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,理莎太太呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:19:30.84,1:19:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,理莎太太怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,1:19:32.63,1:19:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,她去向日葵之家了，我正要去接她
Dialogue: 0,1:19:36.10,1:19:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,那理莎太太一定撐過那些大浪了
Dialogue: 0,1:19:40.02,1:19:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,宗介，也讓我坐
Dialogue: 0,1:19:42.98,1:19:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,久美子，我很忙，下次再說吧
Dialogue: 0,1:19:45.90,1:19:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,向日葵之家的人都在前山公園避難
Dialogue: 0,1:19:49.61,1:19:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,-撐著點啊\N-加油啊
Dialogue: 0,1:19:51.69,1:19:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,等這邊忙完\N我們也會去向日葵之家幫忙
Dialogue: 0,1:19:56.12,1:19:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,期待你們的奮戰
Dialogue: 0,1:20:47.46,1:20:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,波妞，要換蠟燭了
Dialogue: 0,1:20:54.13,1:20:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,沒問題的，我有剛剛拿到的蠟燭
Dialogue: 0,1:20:58.14,1:21:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,好燙，還好燙喔
Dialogue: 0,1:21:06.10,1:21:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,1:21:09.61,1:21:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,波妞
Dialogue: 0,1:21:11.11,1:21:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,妳可以把這個變大嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:21:13.15,1:21:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯，好啊
Dialogue: 0,1:21:20.16,1:21:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,波妞，妳想睡覺嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:21:30.21,1:21:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,波妞
Dialogue: 0,1:21:47.39,1:21:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,波妞
Dialogue: 0,1:22:47.04,1:22:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了，腳碰得到了
Dialogue: 0,1:23:15.98,1:23:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,有路了
Dialogue: 0,1:23:30.08,1:23:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,船變小了！
Dialogue: 0,1:23:33.00,1:23:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,波妞！
Dialogue: 0,1:23:54.02,1:23:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,波妞
Dialogue: 0,1:23:56.27,1:23:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,波妞，起來啊
Dialogue: 0,1:24:00.99,1:24:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,宗介
Dialogue: 0,1:24:08.58,1:24:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,1:24:10.37,1:24:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我還以為波妞要變回金魚了
Dialogue: 0,1:24:25.76,1:24:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,是理莎的車！\N波妞，這裡有理莎的車！
Dialogue: 0,1:24:33.10,1:24:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,理莎！
Dialogue: 0,1:24:38.19,1:24:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,理莎！
Dialogue: 0,1:24:39.94,1:24:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,理莎！
Dialogue: 0,1:24:43.24,1:24:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,理莎！
Dialogue: 0,1:24:47.20,1:24:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,理莎！
Dialogue: 0,1:24:50.16,1:24:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,理莎！
Dialogue: 0,1:24:53.58,1:24:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,理莎
Dialogue: 0,1:24:57.42,1:24:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,理莎！
Dialogue: 0,1:25:02.21,1:25:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,理莎！
Dialogue: 0,1:25:32.24,1:25:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,宗介，你的船
Dialogue: 0,1:25:34.79,1:25:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,宗介，有水從你的眼睛跑出來
Dialogue: 0,1:25:44.38,1:25:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我們去找理莎吧
Dialogue: 0,1:25:46.38,1:25:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,1:26:28.42,1:26:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,（向日葵之家）
Dialogue: 0,1:26:33.51,1:26:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下，我蓋腳的毛巾
Dialogue: 0,1:26:35.18,1:26:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,誰要毛巾啊？
Dialogue: 0,1:26:36.52,1:26:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,妳們快看，是鯨魚先生
Dialogue: 0,1:26:38.23,1:26:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,好壯觀啊！
Dialogue: 0,1:26:40.77,1:26:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,膝蓋也不會痛了
Dialogue: 0,1:26:43.36,1:26:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,對呀，一點也不會害怕
Dialogue: 0,1:26:45.69,1:26:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡是極樂世界嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:26:46.78,1:26:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,難道妳以為是龍宮城呀？
Dialogue: 0,1:26:51.61,1:26:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,各位，請過來集合
Dialogue: 0,1:26:54.95,1:26:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,-好\N-好
Dialogue: 0,1:26:56.41,1:26:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,1:27:00.21,1:27:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,可以奔跑真好啊
Dialogue: 0,1:27:02.33,1:27:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我先走一步啦
Dialogue: 0,1:27:07.63,1:27:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,到了
Dialogue: 0,1:27:11.34,1:27:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,佳代婆婆跑真快
Dialogue: 0,1:27:14.64,1:27:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,各位，請安靜！
Dialogue: 0,1:27:17.14,1:27:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,命運的時刻終於要來臨了
Dialogue: 0,1:27:19.73,1:27:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,宗介和波妞正朝著這裡來
Dialogue: 0,1:27:22.39,1:27:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,唉呀，怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,1:27:23.90,1:27:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,愛的試煉啊？
Dialogue: 0,1:27:25.36,1:27:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,心兒撲通撲通跳耶
Dialogue: 0,1:27:28.44,1:27:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,1:27:29.53,1:27:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,請安靜
Dialogue: 0,1:27:30.94,1:27:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,諸位是這項神聖試煉的見證人
Dialogue: 0,1:27:33.74,1:27:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,請稍安勿躁
Dialogue: 0,1:27:37.53,1:27:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,藤本先生
Dialogue: 0,1:27:38.79,1:27:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你不會打算對他們做什麼壞事吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:27:42.08,1:27:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,1:27:45.21,1:27:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我當然是不會啊
Dialogue: 0,1:27:47.59,1:27:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,只要波妞乖乖睡覺的話
Dialogue: 0,1:27:49.67,1:27:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,1:27:59.72,1:28:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,應該是個好人
Dialogue: 0,1:28:02.10,1:28:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,理莎太太在做什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:28:04.73,1:28:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,看那邊，她一直在跟波妞的媽媽說話
Dialogue: 0,1:28:17.49,1:28:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,理莎太太很難過吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:28:20.24,1:28:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道在說些什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:28:23.00,1:28:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我們叫她看看，理莎太太！
Dialogue: 0,1:28:25.79,1:28:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,-理莎太太！\N-理莎太太！
Dialogue: 0,1:28:34.59,1:28:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,-我們都是站在宗介和波妞那邊的\N-我們都是站在宗介和波妞那邊的
Dialogue: 0,1:28:54.86,1:28:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,-理莎太太\N-理莎太太
Dialogue: 0,1:28:56.11,1:28:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,妳很擔心吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:28:57.53,1:28:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,小宗一定沒事的
Dialogue: 0,1:28:59.95,1:29:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,因為他很堅強啊
Dialogue: 0,1:29:03.45,1:29:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝，請大家幫他們加油
Dialogue: 0,1:29:06.46,1:29:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,就這麼做吧
Dialogue: 0,1:29:15.67,1:29:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,波妞，有隧道
Dialogue: 0,1:29:17.88,1:29:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,（往前山公園）
Dialogue: 0,1:29:19.18,1:29:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,（單向車道，調撥車道）
Dialogue: 0,1:29:20.35,1:29:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,（禁止通行，讓道）
Dialogue: 0,1:29:21.64,1:29:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}（禁止通行）
Dialogue: 0,1:29:33.32,1:29:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我有走過這裡
Dialogue: 0,1:29:36.61,1:29:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,波妞？
Dialogue: 0,1:29:38.16,1:29:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我討厭這裡
Dialogue: 0,1:29:44.20,1:29:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以放開我的手喔
Dialogue: 0,1:30:24.20,1:30:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,啊，波妞！
Dialogue: 0,1:30:44.89,1:30:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,波妞！
Dialogue: 0,1:30:54.02,1:30:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,波妞
Dialogue: 0,1:31:16.96,1:31:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,波妞，妳不能死啊！
Dialogue: 0,1:31:19.71,1:31:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,波妞
Dialogue: 0,1:31:22.18,1:31:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,波妞，醒來啊，波妞
Dialogue: 0,1:31:24.64,1:31:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,噓，不要叫醒她
Dialogue: 0,1:31:28.56,1:31:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,宗介弟弟，你終於來了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:31:30.64,1:31:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,理莎太太和婆婆大家都在等你喔
Dialogue: 0,1:31:34.94,1:31:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,理莎也在嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:31:36.15,1:31:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我一起來，帶著波妞一起來吧
Dialogue: 0,1:31:42.32,1:31:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,波妞就讓她睡吧，安靜的走吧
Dialogue: 0,1:31:45.28,1:31:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,宗介！
Dialogue: 0,1:31:47.74,1:31:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不要被那種人給騙了
Dialogue: 0,1:31:51.20,1:31:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,盡說些好聽話就把大家給騙走了
Dialogue: 0,1:31:54.83,1:31:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,-辰婆婆！\N-我是不會上當的
Dialogue: 0,1:31:58.30,1:32:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,已經沒時間了
Dialogue: 0,1:32:02.09,1:32:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,妳看不見那個嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:32:04.01,1:32:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,月球要是再接近下去，就無法挽回了
Dialogue: 0,1:32:07.89,1:32:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,說謊也要說得像樣點
Dialogue: 0,1:32:11.43,1:32:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,-啊，真是的…\N-宗介，到這兒來！
Dialogue: 0,1:32:14.02,1:32:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,宗介弟弟，一起走吧\N只有你能拯救這世界
Dialogue: 0,1:32:18.02,1:32:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想動粗
Dialogue: 0,1:32:20.86,1:32:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,波妞！
Dialogue: 0,1:32:24.15,1:32:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,哇！妳對親生父親做了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,1:32:33.08,1:32:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,波妞
Dialogue: 0,1:32:34.62,1:32:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,宗介，過來
Dialogue: 0,1:32:37.21,1:32:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不是這樣的！
Dialogue: 0,1:32:44.67,1:32:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,加油！
Dialogue: 0,1:32:48.22,1:32:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,跳啊！
Dialogue: 0,1:33:29.39,1:33:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,妳們…
Dialogue: 0,1:34:25.65,1:34:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,理莎
Dialogue: 0,1:34:26.57,1:34:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,宗介
Dialogue: 0,1:34:27.78,1:34:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,波妞
Dialogue: 0,1:34:34.12,1:34:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,那邊
Dialogue: 0,1:34:35.74,1:34:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡是哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,1:34:47.92,1:34:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你就是宗介吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:34:50.34,1:34:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,妳好，妳是波妞的媽媽嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:34:53.85,1:34:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,1:34:55.39,1:34:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你把波妞帶了回來
Dialogue: 0,1:34:58.31,1:34:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,1:35:00.44,1:35:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,宗介，波妞為了變成人
Dialogue: 0,1:35:03.81,1:35:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,打開了魔法之蓋
Dialogue: 0,1:35:06.98,1:35:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,她需要一個能接受真實的她的男孩
Dialogue: 0,1:35:14.53,1:35:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道波妞本來是魚嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:35:19.00,1:35:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,1:35:19.91,1:35:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,因為舔了你的血，她成了半人魚
Dialogue: 0,1:35:23.92,1:35:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,原來波妞是舔了我
Dialogue: 0,1:35:28.63,1:35:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,才變半人魚
Dialogue: 0,1:35:32.18,1:35:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,就算波妞是半人魚，你都能接受嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:35:36.18,1:35:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯，不管波妞是魚
Dialogue: 0,1:35:38.43,1:35:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,半人魚還是人類，我全都喜歡
Dialogue: 0,1:35:56.83,1:35:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,波妞，過來這邊
Dialogue: 0,1:36:13.43,1:36:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,他願意當一個完全接受妳的人
Dialogue: 0,1:36:20.93,1:36:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,當人類就要捨棄魔法
Dialogue: 0,1:36:25.27,1:36:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,妳願意嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:36:27.23,1:36:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,1:36:37.20,1:36:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,回到陸地後，請親吻這個氣泡
Dialogue: 0,1:36:41.08,1:36:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,波妞就會變成一個五歲的女孩
Dialogue: 0,1:36:48.21,1:36:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,波妞，太好了
Dialogue: 0,1:36:51.21,1:36:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝妳，波妞的媽媽
Dialogue: 0,1:36:59.72,1:37:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,各位，世界的裂縫要閉合了
Dialogue: 0,1:37:06.77,1:37:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,小宗真了不起
Dialogue: 0,1:37:08.52,1:37:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,宗介
Dialogue: 0,1:37:10.90,1:37:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,宗介
Dialogue: 0,1:37:14.78,1:37:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,宗介
Dialogue: 0,1:37:40.47,1:37:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,理莎，謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,1:37:42.68,1:37:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,也謝謝妳，曼瑪蓮！
Dialogue: 0,1:37:56.86,1:37:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:38:04.87,1:38:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我現在去拿輪椅來
Dialogue: 0,1:38:07.08,1:38:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不用啦，我們會自己走
Dialogue: 0,1:38:09.50,1:38:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,真熱鬧
Dialogue: 0,1:38:15.09,1:38:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,這是你的船吧？還給你
Dialogue: 0,1:38:19.30,1:38:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,啊，謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,1:38:20.93,1:38:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,之前種種很抱歉\N可以跟你握個手嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:38:30.60,1:38:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,波妞就托付給你了
Dialogue: 0,1:38:34.98,1:38:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,是耕一的船！
Dialogue: 0,1:38:41.03,1:38:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,耕一！
Dialogue: 0,1:38:46.70,1:38:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,啊，是理莎，宗介也在
Dialogue: 0,1:38:52.21,1:38:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,波妞，那是耕一的船喔
Dialogue: 0,1:39:16.19,1:39:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,波妞，魚的小寶貝
Dialogue: 0,1:39:19.94,1:39:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,從蔚藍的海洋而來
Dialogue: 0,1:39:24.16,1:39:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,波妞，胖嘟嘟起來
Dialogue: 0,1:39:27.87,1:39:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,肚子圓滾滾的小女孩
Dialogue: 0,1:39:40.17,1:39:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,跳一跳，踏一踏
Dialogue: 0,1:39:44.18,1:39:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,有腳真好啊！到處跑一跑
Dialogue: 0,1:39:48.14,1:39:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,握一握，揮一揮
Dialogue: 0,1:39:52.14,1:39:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,有手真好啊！快來手牽手
Dialogue: 0,1:39:56.40,1:40:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,和她一起跳舞
Dialogue: 0,1:40:00.19,1:40:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我胸口碰碰跳
Dialogue: 0,1:40:04.16,1:40:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,親一個，啾啾
Dialogue: 0,1:40:06.16,1:40:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,抱一下，啾啾
Dialogue: 0,1:40:08.70,1:40:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我最喜歡她了
Dialogue: 0,1:40:14.12,1:40:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,紅通通的
Dialogue: 0,1:40:16.25,1:40:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,波妞，魚的小寶貝
Dialogue: 0,1:40:19.92,1:40:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,從蔚藍的海洋而來
Dialogue: 0,1:40:24.18,1:40:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,波妞，胖嘟嘟起來
Dialogue: 0,1:40:27.93,1:40:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,肚子圓滾滾的小女孩
Dialogue: 0,1:40:39.73,1:40:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,（全劇終）
